 {\"sentence\": \"Dressel, 27, said his relaxed demeanor on deck in Indianapolis has belied some tense moments behind the scenes.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.8771237964703502, \"rank\": 0.09040614412526055, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"his relaxed demeanor\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1477}, {\"ngram\": \"deck\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"some tense moments\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"the scenes\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is parts of this meet, I have had some very low lows,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parts\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"this meet\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"some very low lows\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is parts in my hotel room that are not on camera, talking with my wife, talking with my therapist - it has not been smooth sailing this whole meet.\\\"\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parts\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1638}, {\"ngram\": \"my hotel room\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1655}, {\"ngram\": \"camera\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1678}, {\"ngram\": \"my wife\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"my therapist\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"smooth sailing\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"this whole meet\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, he added, he's trying to relish the good times after his extended break that refreshed his relationship to the sport.\", \"from\":